# 📊 Data Cleaning & Reporting Automation

## 🔹 Overview
Automates data cleaning, processing, and report generation using Python.

## ⚙️ Features
- Remove duplicates
- Handle missing values
- Standardize data
- Generate Excel reports
- Create visual charts

## 🛠 Tools Used
Python, Pandas, Matplotlib, Excel

## 📈 Output
- Clean dataset
- Sales report (Excel)
- Sales visualization chart

## 🚀 Result
Reduces manual work and improves reporting efficiency.